# Horizontal Gradient Background Demo

Output examples/svgs/backgrounds/horizontal-gradient.svg

Set FontSize 16
Set Template macos
Set Theme dracula
Set Background "gradient(#ff1b6b, #45caff:horizontal)"
Set BackgroundPadding 25

Type "echo 'Horizontal gradient!'"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Type "Three colors: purple to pink"
Sleep 1s
